parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle's steering wander and death wobble can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle's steering wheel shakes or vibrates violently
making it difficult to maintain control; the vehicle wanders or drifts to one side; the steering wheel feels loose or has excessive play; the vehicle experiences a sudden loss of power steering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the driver to lose control of the vehicle, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle's power steering system fails
making it difficult to steer; the vehicle's steering wheel becomes heavy or hard to turn; the vehicle's power steering warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering damper can cause the vehicle's steering to become unstable, leading to accidents or near-misses, especially at high speeds.
